public class GammaKDEDistribution

Author:
Jennifer Tom Based on S. X. Chen. Probability density function estimation using gamma kernels. Annals of the Institute of Statistical Mathematics, 52(3):471-480, 2000. Use to create KDE for positive valued functions Assumes limits are (0, inf) Must provide with a bandwidth, or defaults to Scott's Rule Univariate distribution only
